OL,3,CEight-year-old girl battling cancer
OL,4,Cwho broke UK birthday card record dies
OL,6,FAn eight-year-old girl who had stage
OL,7,Ffour cancer and achieved her wish of
OL,8,Fbreaking the UK record for the most
OL,9,Fbirthday cards received has died.
OL,11,FAmelia Kolpa, from Rowley Regis in the
OL,12,FBlack Country, had been receiving
OL,13,Fpalliative care for a stage four
OL,14,Fneuroblastoma and had been in and out
OL,15,Fof hospital since the age of two-and-a-
OL,16,Fhalf.
OL,18,FShe went through just under two years
OL,19,Fof intensive treatment, including
OL,20,Fchemotherapy, immunotherapy and
OL,21,Fradiotherapy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
