PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773846665
OL,3,CEight-year-old girl battling cancer
OL,4,Cwho broke UK birthday card record dies
OL,6,FHer mum Katarzyna Bartczak announced
OL,7,FAmelia's death on Tuesday evening on
OL,8,Fsocial media.
OL,10,FThe post reads: "Our dearest Amelia,
OL,11,Fyou were and always will be our
OL,12,Fgreatest miracle. Our heart. Our light.
OL,14,F"Thank you for every moment, every
OL,15,Fsmile, every glance... for the love
OL,16,Fyou taught us.
OL,18,F"This is not goodbye... it's 'see you
OL,19,Fagain'."
OL,26,@{D@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
