FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773846665
OL,3,CEight-year-old girl battling cancer
OL,4,Cwho broke UK birthday card record dies
OL,6,FHer wish for her birthday on Tuesday,
OL,7,FMarch 3, was to receive 8,000 birthday
OL,8,Fcards, but through the help of the
OL,9,Fcommunity, she ended up receiving more
OL,10,Fthan 300,000 cards for the occasion.
OL,12,FITV News Central went along to film in
OL,13,FFebruary when a thousand motorcyclists
OL,14,Ffrom a Black Country biker group
OL,15,Fgathered outside her house to hand
OL,16,Fdeliver the cards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773846665
OL,3,CEight-year-old girl battling cancer
OL,4,Cwho broke UK birthday card record dies
OL,6,FAmelia's family also organised a group
OL,7,Fdance in March inside the Merry Hill
OL,8,Fshopping centre, in Dudley, which
OL,9,Finvolved members of the public coming
OL,10,Ftogether to do a mass Macarena.
OL,12,FHighfields Primary School issued a
OL,13,Fstatement which said Amelia was 'a
OL,14,Fspecial part' of the school community.
OL,16,FThe statement reads: "Throughout
OL,17,Feverything she faced, Amelia showed
OL,18,Fincredible strength and courage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773846665
OL,3,CEight-year-old girl battling cancer
OL,4,Cwho broke UK birthday card record dies
OL,6,F"What so many of us will remember
OL,7,Fmost, however, is her beautiful smile.
OL,8,FIt was the kind of smile that brought
OL,9,Fwarmth and happiness to everyone
OL,10,Faround her.
OL,12,F"Her positivity, determination and
OL,13,Fgentle spirit touched the hearts of
OL,14,Fcountless staff and children across
OL,15,Fthe school."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
